      { title: "Preparing for a Hurricane", steps: ["Weather forecasters issue a hurricane watch for the coastal area.", "Residents buy supplies including water, batteries, canned food, and plywood.", "Families board up windows and move outdoor furniture inside.", "The governor orders a mandatory evacuation for low-lying zones.", "Residents drive inland and check into shelters or stay with relatives.", "After the hurricane passes, families return home to assess any damage."] },
